title: Episode 573 | "Go To Bed"
description:
On this week's episode, the guys discuss the newest developments with Kanye West's brand fallouts (14:25). Joe remains adamant about Alec Baldwin's arrest after his 1-year post regarding the shooting (35:55), the guys discuss Madonna's legacy and superstar status (43:55). Ice is excited for Drake and 21 Savage's new album (1:09:10). Next, Joe asks how the guys deal with clingy girlfriends (1:25:15), the guys also discuss side chicks (1:40:55), and Gillie and Wallo's new deal (2:05:00).
